con:testCase.name: GET_learningloop_Asset
con:testCase.con:description: TestCase generated for REST Resource [Assets] located at [/api/v1/learningLoop/${#Project#learningloop}/objectives/${#Project#objective}/assets]

con:config.script:
import jxl.* def NumOfXLSRows
def XLPath = testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.getPropertyValue("XLPath1")
log.info ("Path : " + XLPath) Workbook objWB = Workbook.getWorkbook(new File(XLPath)) Sheet objSheet = objWB.getSheet(0) NumOfXLSRows = objSheet.getRows() log.info ("Number of TZ_Xls rows: " + NumOfXLSRows) learningloop = objSheet.getCell(0,1).getContents() objective = objSheet.getCell(1,1).getContents()
log.info("learningloop_Value: " + learningloop) log.info("objective_Value: " + objective)
testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.setPropertyValue("learningloop", learningloop) testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.setPropertyValue("objective", objective)
objWB.close()
